videos.description: Marina Mabrey drives the length of the floor and makes the layup after being fouled to extend Notre Dame's lead over Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Mabrey goes coast to coast for layup

videos.description: Notre Dame's Arike Ogunbowale drives through the contact and makes the layup after being fouled.
videos.headline: Notre Dame continues to attack the basket

videos.description: Kathryn Westbeld hits Brianna Turner with the quick pass for the easy bucket down low.
videos.headline: Great ball movement leads to bucket for Irish

videos.description: Arike Ogunbowale takes the entry pass and finishes the easy layup inside the paint.
videos.headline: Notre Dame continues to dominate the paint

videos.description: Lindsay Allen makes the layup after being fouled on the fast break.
videos.headline: Notre Dame scores on fast break
